	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <span id= >Anonymous</span><br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Excellent [4.66]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>IF this is your first charcter or even your first caster you might want to try a couple of group type casters (clerics, druids, shamans, before playing an Enchanter. This class is the most difficult and rewarding in the game.&nbsp;&nbsp;Im going to give you tips on soloing up til level 10 when you are considered a newbie. (Note this is not a complete guide and is better suited to the newer player.  I apologize for the short level range but I will update)<br><br>LV 1-3 During these Levels just kill everything white and blue.   Kill loot sell kill Loot sell kill.  If your having trouble you might want to buy the Weaken Spell and lower it's strength.  Although many people saay our pets aren't at all useful use it at lv 1 if you have it.  Even at 2 and 3 it can be used to take the blows you would be taking making this level bracket go along quicker.<br><br>LV 4-7 These Levels you want to go out and explore the world.  You now have acess to Gate which alows you to teleport to your bind spot.  Suffocating Sphere is a nice upgrade to Shallow breath. Haze grants more AC.  Also Enfeeblement lowers strength and I believe their AC too.  Now you also have the spell the makes enchanters enchanters, Mesmerize. Use it. Use it often.  This spell enables you to take on 2 white mobs(wih your new lv 4-5 pet of course) as long as you have enough mana.  As soon as you damage a mob it will wake up though but you can debuff using Enfeeblement and Tashan.  <br><br>lV 8-10  You now have a dd spell called Chaotic Feedback which averages about 43 points of damage.  You have 4 racial illusions total now and a new pet spell which from now on wll be in Highhold keep.  Even though you can now cripple your targets using Root, Mezmerize, Tashan and Enfeebelment it's not dead yet.  Dont get cocky like I did and lose your level.  Remember you dont get your rise of power til 30 +.  At these levels use the same tactics you did and dont solo unless you are sure of yourself and full health and mana.  Use Mesmerize then root the mob along with tashan enfeeblement and then nuke them to death, but save some mana in case you have to make an emergency gate.  I have to end now so I can go aback and learn more about this wonderful class, but I will update ASAP.</p>&nbsp;<br> </td></td></tr>
