	     <tr><td valign=top id=fs8 class=mform><span id=notbold>By:</span> <a href=poster.html?user=40732><span id=Scholar>Rimailkall</span></a><br><b><span id=Scholar>Scholar</span></b><br><span id=notbold>19 posts<br><span id=notbold>Score</span>: Decent [3.00]</td><td valign=top class=mform width=100%><p>You have to go to Kunark to get breeze.&nbsp;&nbsp;Take the shuttles from Butcherblock dock and that will put you on another boat (it's huge), which will take you to Kunark, Fironia Vie.  It's a safe area for good races and there is a merchant that sells the spell, and a bank there.  If you go, you may as well bind yourself there because Lake of Ill Omen is a good place for a level 16 chanter to hang out.</p>&nbsp;<br>Semper Fi!</td></td></tr>
